text: Madeleine Front (born 22 April 1930) is a French alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Possibly living people Category:French female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of France Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Savoie
